# Go build output
/bin/
/dist/
*.exe
*.test
*.out
# Compiled control-plane binary (`go build ./cmd/msb-manager` drops it at the
# repo root). Anchored with a leading slash so it matches ONLY the root-level
# binary — an unanchored `msb-manager` also matches the cmd/msb-manager/
# package directory and silently ignores its source (e.g. main_test.go).
/msb-manager

# Go workspace
go.work
go.work.sum

# Secrets / config — never commit
*-secrets.yml
secrets.yml
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
credentials

# Editor / OS
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store

# Local Claude state
.claude/

# Handoff brief — local working note, not version controlled
HANDOFF.md
